cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.LG 

This paper discusses the concept of Age-of-Information (AoI) in the context of Internet of Things (IoT) networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves optimization and control aspects, which suggest the categories cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.MA (Multiagent Systems). Finally, the paper uses mathematical modeling and analysis, which could also fit into the category cs.LG (Machine Learning).
